data.description: Owner related to agent. Buy your own little slice of the Jim Ned Valley! With views of Bald Eagle Mountain and convenient access to the highway you can be in Tuscola in about 3 minutes and Abilene in 20 minutes. This lot comes with an AEP transformer already installed, a water meter from Steamboat Mountain Water already purchased and very little, if any, leveling needed. One single family dwelling allowed on each lot, no restrictions on size or building materials. Deed restrictions will allow for new mobile or modular homes as long as they are permanently affixed and skirted within 60 days of placement.
